tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE voice_search_suggestions (
    suggestion_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    suggestion_text VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    suggestion_rank INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR,
    last_name VARCHAR,
    email VARCHAR,
    phone_number VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE voice_command_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    command_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
